Enumerations

Detailed Description

The section has a list of all internal data structures which are used internally by the SPI module.

Typedef Documentation

typedef struct MibSpi_DMAReqlineCfg_t MibSpi_DMAReqlineCfg

SPI Driver DMA request line configuration.

The structure is used to store the hardware specific configuration for DMA request lines.

typedef struct MibSpi_driverDmaInfo_t MibSpi_driverDmaInfo

SPI Driver Info for Master.

The structure is used to store the driver info for Master.

typedef struct MibSpi_HwCfg_t MibSpi_HwCfg

SPI Driver HW configuration.

The structure is used to store the hardware specific configuration which is passed to SPI driver instance

typedef enum MibSpi_transferType_e MibSpi_transferType

SPI Driver Transfer type.

The structure is used to store the internal transfer type

typedef struct MibSpiDriver_Object_t MibSpiDriver_Object

SPI Driver Object.

The structure is used to store the SPI driver internal variables. The application must not access any member variables of this structure!

typedef struct MibSpiDriverHWStats_t MibSpiDriverHWStats

SPI Driver Statistics.

The structure is used to store driver statistics

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum MibSpi_transferType_e

SPI Driver Transfer type.

The structure is used to store the internal transfer type
